    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day I picked it up! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is still totally spotless. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
