    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, with the double-VANOS system meticulously serviced and the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response. Power is delivered through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is exceptional; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension retains factory-spec damping with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turn-key collector-grade machine optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
