      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the wide-body, naturally aspirated 911 era. Featuring the robust 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, the power plant delivers linear torque and a visceral acoustic profile. The chassis is anchored by the Turbo-spec suspension geometry and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers, ensuring exceptional thermal management and bite. This example boasts a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently refreshed clutch assembly. The six-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, while the all-wheel-drive system provides superior mechanical grip and high-speed stability. With pristine factory paint depth and a flawlessly preserved cabin, this is a turn-key collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
